New Zealand coastline.

Source: R/data.R
nz.Rd

New Zealand coastline, excluding the Chathams, that is simplified for ggplot.

nz

Format

An sf object.

Source

https://data.linz.govt.nz/layer/51153-nz-coastlines-and-islands-polygons-topo-150k/
